reviewText: A great video that was more entertaining than expected.

Be prepared for more than you anticipated.  If you don't like to see naked men, don't buy it.  I am 80 years old and still WANT - as Barbara Stanwyck said in "The Thorn Birds". Why must all voyeurism be aimed at "perfect" female bodies?  This film is sheer delight for the mature and realistic individual - gay and straight.  Great choice!
